snippet.title: TheTimelessWonder
snippet.description:
The message of The Timeless Wonder points to a nondual reality, which is recognized as the natural reality. There is no 'I' living its own life. There is no entity called 'me' existing as an individual. All there is, is wholeness appearing as this.

Andreas offers Live-Video-Chats, Talks and Retreats.

www.thetimelesswonder.com
